ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: A code that is used to identify the property. The code is used in ValueSet.expansion.contains.property.code.

ivardefs.name: uri
ivardefs.desc: Reference to the formal meaning of the property. One possible source of meaning is the [Concept Properties](codesystem-concept-properties.html) code system.

properties.desc: A property defines an additional slot through which additional information can be provided about a concept.
